{"tid":1164082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"波音首認737-MAX軟件有缺陷","createTime":"2019-05-20T23:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T00:38:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aed47eb150812dc5434ef5e0d45977e58997d1d9","tid":1164082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T23:24:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190520/20682610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F20682610&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWba%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=5f6257f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F20682610&h=38aa4647\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190520/20682610</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n波音首認737-MAX軟件有缺陷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190520/large/20wx7p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190520%2Flarge%2F20wx7p.jpg&h=721dda6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先後經歷兩宗嚴重空難後，波音公司前日終於首次承認其737-MAX（圖）客機飛行訓練軟件存有設計缺陷，昨稱已完成修復，但未提及公司何時發現問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未能模擬兩宗空難情況<br />\n<br />\n波音前日發聲明，指737-MAX模擬飛行訓練軟件，未能模擬出今年3月埃塞俄比亞航空空難或去年10月獅子航空空難時的個別飛行情況。兩宗空難跟機動特性增強系統（MCAS）有關。<br />\n<br />\n最新的修正改善了模擬手動配平輪（manual trim wheel）的力度負荷。它主要用於在空中調節飛機飛行角度。「波音就有關改動和修正，跟儀器生產商及監管當局緊密合作，確保模擬飛行訓練軟件可展示全部飛行情況。」<br />\n<br />\n但航空業界消息人士指，只有加拿大航空公司擁有MAX模擬飛行訓練軟件，美國的航空公司只用波音較舊款737NG的模擬飛行訓練軟件，訓練機師駕駛737-MAX。737-MAX客機最大用家美國西南航空公司指，這是因為波音以往一直強調NG和MAX相差不大，惟737NG正正沒有MCAS。西南航空預期「今年稍後」可獲首套737-MAX模擬飛行訓練軟件。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/德新社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n澳總理靠單人騷爆冷 鞏固地位<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n伊朗生物科學家赴美變「人質」"},{"pid":"0652c636ae11744dcfc2aab511b3687488e319d6","tid":1164082,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T23:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545d3188652262068e38febc21a0cf4c18e4cb70","tid":1164082,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T23:56:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7efd9126dbc7c60c7f9bbda89ab862b1c5bd3c41","tid":1164082,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"545d3188652262068e38febc21a0cf4c18e4cb70","tid":1164082,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T23:56:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:09:58.000Z","msg":"應該告到甩褲添"},{"pid":"cd308f100660d4eab169282117dcdae6c6d35a5f","tid":1164082,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"545d3188652262068e38febc21a0cf4c18e4cb70","tid":1164082,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T23:56:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:11:10.000Z","msg":"一定得，美國唔係香港"},{"pid":"9328de1ab8c91bc8d9a33730a45d0119347bbf46","tid":1164082,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:20:05.000Z","msg":"有無專家解釋下關個訓練系統咩事？"},{"pid":"2f2cb4b415d23afc6a7221c732dda30ec271c86a","tid":1164082,"uid":123724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9328de1ab8c91bc8d9a33730a45d0119347bbf46","tid":1164082,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:20:05.000Z","msg":"有無專家解釋下關個訓練系統咩事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:30:13.000Z","msg":"因為無套737max 訓練系統,波音無得特別強調有新野加左,啲機師/公司只係用old version做training都唔覺有問題,所以根本唔aware 737 max 有新既 function （正正係佢出事果嗰）,所以啲機師死左都唔知咩事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正"},{"pid":"c96fa2d5cabc1e49dfc70cde1cb41de22fdb9ae8","tid":1164082,"uid":37924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:38:33.000Z","msg":"認左好耐啦 飛機競賽 <br />\nairbus出完波音又急急腳出架max <br />\n但機翼clearance又唔夠擺個大啲既引擎 <br />\n唯有升高個引擎 <br />\n個所謂training course都係就咁用部ipad篤幾野<br />\n更加唔好講冇提及MCAS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}